The paper deals with image steganography and proposes a novel approach that utilizes a steganalysis convolutional neural network (CNN) framework. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper deals with security and cryptography, which could fall under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The proposed approach involves optimizing the embedding process, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
